      "rdf:value": "<L>148252<pc>745,3<k1>Band<k2>Band<e>1\r\n<s>Band</s> ¦ <ab>cl.</ab> 1. <ab>Ā.</ab> (<ls>Dhātup. ii, 11</ls>) <s>Ba/ndate</s>, to be greeted with praise, receive applause, <ls>RV.</ls> (<ls>L.</ls> also = to be or make fortunate or excellent; to be or make glad; to shine; to honour or worship) :\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/><ab>Caus.</ab> <s>Bandayati</s>, to cause to prosper, <ls>Dhātup. xxxii, 50</ls>; <ls>Vop.</ls><info westergaard=\"Badi,2.11,01.0012;Baqi,32.50,10.0046\"/><info whitneyroots=\"Band,109\"/><info verb=\"genuineroot\" cp=\"1Ā\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
