      "rdf:value": "<L>54101<pc>5-0201<k1>Band<k2>Band\n{#Band#}¦, {#Ba/ndate#} so <ab>v. a.</ab> {#arcati#}\n<ls>NAIGH. 3,14.</ls>\n<ls>NIR. 5,2.</ls>\n<ls>DHĀTUP. 2,11</ls> ({#kalyARe suKe caH mutprItyoH SuBe#}\n<ls>VOP.</ls>). {%jauchzenden Zuruf —, Lob empfangen%}: {#A Banda^mAne\\ upA^ke\\ nakto\\zAsA^#} ({#sIdatAm#})\n<ls>ṚV. 1,142,7.</ls> <ls n=\"ṚV.\">3,4,6.</ls> {#vE\\SvA\\na\\raH pra\\tnaTA\\ nAka\\mAru^haddi\\vaspf\\zWaM Banda^mAnaH su\\manma^BiH#}\n<ls n=\"ṚV. 3,\">2,12.</ls> {#A vi^veSa\\ roda^sI\\ BUri^varpasA purupri\\yo Ba^ndate\\ DAma^BiH ka\\viH#}\n<ls n=\"ṚV. 3,\">3,4.</ls> Angeblich auch so <ab>v. a.</ab> {#jvalati#}\n<ls>NAIGH. 1,16.</ls> {#Banda/yati#} ({#kalyARe#})\n<ls>VOP.</ls> in <ls>DHĀTUP. 32,50.</ls>\n<div n=\"v\">— <ab>Vgl.</ab> {#Badra#} .\n<LEND>"
    },
